description:
Offers: 

Monthly Salary: $15,000 or above which includes basic salary and different allowances;
5 days work per week, 8.5 hours / day;
3 months On-the-job training with salary at Fixed Office Hours;
14 days annual leave;
Discretionary bonus;
Excellent Career development opportunities.

Responsibilities:   

Handle the incoming telephone call from the airline members;
NO Cold Call and NO Selling;
Answer inquiries in professional and efficient manner;
Cooperate with other teams members to resolve customer's request efficiently.

Requirements: 

Form 5 or Post-Secondary or above;
Fluent in Cantonese, Mandarin and English is a MUST;
Willing to work shift duty and on roster basis;
Previous customer service OR related experience;
Fresh graduate with Summer Job / Internship experience will also be considered;
Customer-oriented with passion, patience and caring attitude;
Good interpersonal and communication skills.


Candidates with Fluent Japanese or Korean Language can be consider as Foreigner Language Team and get extra $1,500 Monthly Language Allowance.

Attractive remuneration package commensurate with qualifications and experience will be offered to the right candidate.  Interested parties please use the following "APPLY NOW" function to apply for the job.  A full resume stating date of availability, current & expected salary are required.

Or email the Full Resume to dave @ talentcl.com

For any further inquiries about the job, please feel free to send message by WhatsApp at 9165 3366 (No telephone call will be answer).

All personal data collected will be used for recruitment purpose only.  Applicants not hearing from us within 3 weeks may consider their applications unsuccessful.

圓核秀都總部設立於香港，自2012年以來不斷探索和拓展在中國大陸的娛樂演藝秀業務，通過收購、原創和改編等方式積累了大量娛樂演藝秀強IP群，涵蓋了大中小型娛樂演藝秀和室內外沉浸式燈光秀等不同類型的產品,並形成了具有自身特色的娛樂演藝消費場景品牌——《秀都》。《秀都》品牌專案融合演藝高科技手段，滿足大眾消費轉型升級和振興夜間經濟的需求，高效佈局於中國大流量旅遊目的地城市。

我們為合適的候選人提供有吸引力的薪水和附加福利。如有興趣，請將完整的中文簡歷，現有和預期的薪資待遇和可上班日期發送電郵或致電25988292 陳小姐洽。

崗位職責:


為在香港，英屬維爾京群島，開曼群島，中國及其他司法管轄區註冊成立、續期、變更登記、注消的本集團公司及合夥企業履行全面的公司秘書職責;
處理臨時公司專案並與內部部門和外部各方(包括律師、公證人、審計師和代理人)協調;
管理集團公司結構並為總部準備報告;
準備中英文會議記錄，處理與投資專案和資金有關的權益披露;
協助為公司治理，法律，風險和內部合規職能提供一般秘書和文書支援;
維護和更新法定記錄和適當的備案;
協助管理內部和外部合同檔的備案系統;
協助組織委員會，董事會和股東大會以及準備會議記錄;
協助起草和編制公告，通告和年度及中期報告;
在需要時協助管理工作和臨時任務。
根據需要執行臨時分配。


要求:

獲得認可香港或內地主修本科學士學位或以上；
ICSA / HKICS會員優先
至少2年相關工作經驗;  必須具備文化旅遊業、傳媒、市場行銷、酒店管理、主題公園等行業的專業工作經驗，熟悉IPO 程序及相關知識優先;
在集團內可自主工作的能力;熟悉并能善用內地格式及詞彙;
優秀的書面和口頭溝通技巧(需要普通話和英語);
自我啟動，積極主動，適應能力強，可以明確劃分優先順序並管理多個專案;
需具備表達個人意見能力;
有高度的誠信、專業、成長的意願，能夠在快節奏的環境中工作，並能夠滿足最後期限及具備優秀的中文寫作技巧

職責
迎接客人並協助客人上落車並將客人送到目的地;
為客人打開豪華轎車車門，為有特別需要人士如長者提供幫忙;
幫助客人裝卸行李，並將行李帶入機場和酒店;
日常清潔與維護維修保養及牌照繢期;
定期檢查車輪狀況，節約燃油，保障行車安全;
記錄上下客信息和提交日報。
Job responsibilites

Greet and drive guest to destinations;
Provide special assistance to guests with special needs such as the elderly;
Assist Guests load and unload luggage when embarking and disembarking in airport and hotel;
Daily cleaning and maintenance;
Ensuring driving safety;
Create daily driving logs.
入職要求

持有有效駕駛執照(1號);
具至少3年相關經驗, 曾從事旅遊業者優先考慮;
中五程度以上;
良好英語及普通話能力;
可輪班工作。

Requirements

Hold valid Driving License No.1;
Not less than 3 years relevant experience; worked in travel industry is an advantage;
Completion of Secondary 5;
Good at English and Putonghua;
Can work on shift.

Job Description

Handle email and phone inquiries on a daily basis, and entertain visiting clients from time to time;
Generate new business opportunities and close project deals, mostly by by email and over the phone;
Coordinate with internal and external linguists, and monitor their progress if need be;
Develop strong ties with key clients and linguists, and maintain client database and project archive.

 Requirements

Tertiary educated in hospitality, business, marketing or other related disciplines;
At least 3 years of full-time experience in sales/customer services (suitable candidates with lesser experience will be considered for the post of Customer Service Executive);
Keen interest in honing language skills an added advantage;
Good negotiation and communication skills;
Mature, multi-tasking and self-initiative with good business sense;
Competent in English and Putonghua as well as Cantonese. 

 If interested, please send your CV with expected salary to Miss Lam. To know more about us, please visit our website at www.yaoshun.com.hk.

